==About==
===Format===
* '''Pre-Quarters:''''' July 18th - 21st, 2026
** 64 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 32 qualified teams.
*** 32 invited teams.
*** Each group will play 6 matches.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams from each group (Total 32 teams)}} advance to Quarter Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams from each group}} are eliminated.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''''' July 22th - 23th, 2026
** 32 teams, 2 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 2 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 6 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 4 teams from each group (Total 8 teams)}} advance to Grand Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 12 teams from each group (Total 24 teams)}} advance to Semi Finals.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' July 24th - 26th, 2026
** 24 teams, 3 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Round-robin format.
** Each group will play 12 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} advance to the Grand Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|down|The rest}} are eliminated.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' July 27th - 29th, 2026
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

